But most of the time, when pard doubles, you will not have enough to convert to penalty. 
1NT-X-pass-2@c
So you will run to ^*B2@C^*n
This says nothing about your clubs, only that you want partner to be able to bid his long suit
Your hand is    xxxx, J10xx, xx, xxx. 
You MUST bid 2@C and let pard pick the trump suit|
