at|

a) You have ^*U3 cards^*N in the suit he bid: ^*BPass^*N (or raise with 4 card support).  
If you have a strong hand, you may look for game, but remember that partner possibly has a "weak freak"|
pg| ***** 163 ***** |


at|

b) If you have ^*Ufewer than 3^*N cards: bid the ^*Bcheapest suit in which you have at least 3 cards^*N.
Pard will pass or correct to his second suit.
Sometimes you will have to scramble or play in a 5-2 fit. That's life!|
