at| 

c) When you have a ^*Ufit^*N, bid as high as you can as fast as you can, using the ^*BLaw of Total Tricks (LOTT)^*N. 
Which says you are (usually) safe to bid to the same level as the total number of trumps you and your partner have.
This is why DONT requires 5-5 or a very good 5-4 hand to bid. 
Your partner is expected to push the bidding with a fit!|
